         <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title">
          <a data-analytics-link="feature" data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" href="https://tn.chalkbeat.org/2021/3/19/22340780/memphis-scs-covid-treadwell-one-year-later">
           These Memphis schools were the first to get a COVID scare last year. Their experiences warned of the challenges to come.
          </a>

          <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title">
           <a data-analytics-link="article" data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" href="https://www.chalkbeat.org/2021/3/19/22340072/cdc-six-three-feet-distancing-schools-covid">

           </a>
          </h2>

            <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title">
             <a data-analytics-link="feature" data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" href="https://ny.chalkbeat.org/2021/3/19/22337070/ipads-nyc-doe-english-learners">
              NYC gave thousands of students iPads. For English learners, those devices have not been up to the task.
             </a>
            </h2>
            <p class="p-dek c-entry-box--compact__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">
             Were watching our students struggle with technology not designed to help them learn.
            </p>

            <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title">
             <a data-analytics-link="feature" data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" href="https://ny.chalkbeat.org/2021/3/12/22326063/dez-ann-romain-brooklyn-democracy-academy-principal-death-coronavirus-anniversary">
              A daunting, dark and difficult time: How a Brooklyn school moved forward after losing its leader to COVID
             </a>
            </h2>
            <p class="p-dek c-entry-box--compact__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">
             Brooklyn Democracy Academy Principal Dez-Ann Romain died of the coronavirus. Heres how her NYC school persevered after losing their leader to COVID-19.
            </p>

            <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title">
             <a data-analytics-link="feature" data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" href="https://www.chalkbeat.org/2020/12/22/22193775/states-public-school-enrollment-decline-covid">
              Across U.S., states see public school enrollment dip as virus disrupts education
             </a>
            </h2>
            <p class="p-dek c-entry-box--compact__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">
             Data from 33 states shows that K-12 public school enrollment has dropped across those states by more than a half a million students since the same time last year.
            </p>
            <div class="c-byline" data-cdata='{"timestamp":1608616800}' data-cid="site/byline-1616403267_916_97047">
             <span class="c-byline-wrapper">

              <span class="c-byline__item">

                <span class="c-byline__author-name">
                 Kalyn Belsha
                </span>
               </a>
               ,
               <a data-analytics-link="author-name" href="https://www.chalkbeat.org/authors/gabrielle-lamarr-lemee">
                <span class="c-byline__author-name">
                 Gabrielle LaMarr LeMee
                </span>
               </a>
               , and 2 more
              </span>
              <span class="c-byline__item">
               <time class="c-byline__item" data-relative-timestamp="true" data-ui="timestamp" datetime="2020-12-22T06:00:00">
                December 22, 2020
               </time>
              </span>

        var dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        dataLayer
          .filter(function(m) { return !!m['Network'] })
          .forEach(function(m) {
            Object.keys(m).forEach(function(k) { data[k] = m[k] });
          });

        var userid = data['Logged in Status'];
        data['User ID'] = (typeof userid === 'number') ? userid : null;
        phonographEvents.push(['pageload', data]);
      })();
  </script>
  <!-- End Phonograph -->
  <script src="https://cdn.broadstreetads.com/init-2.min.js">
  </script>
  <script>
   broadstreet.watch({ networkId: 6336 })
  </script>
  <broadstreet-zone zone-id="84235">
  </broadstreet-zone>
 </body>
</html>
